Gateway's 2012 - 2013 Kick Off

Jack Reznicki Presents

Lighting and Perception

Tuesday September 11, 2012 7:30 PM


 

Please join us on Tuesday September 11th as Gateway celebrates its 50th Birthday.· Jack Reznicki will help us kick off our new year. Humor, wit, and more than a passing familiarity with the absurd have all helped Jack Reznicki become one of the most sought-after illustrative photographers in New York and one of the most popular program presenters in the photo community. Over his 30-year career, he may be best known for his expressive photographs of kids or as he says, “Kids as kids”. ··It promises to be a very exciting evening.

 

GCC meets at  St. Andrews Church in Framingham. Guests are welcome!

 

Address
Three Maple Street
Framingham, MA 01702
